data.description: Stunning, Model Perfect 1 Story Home in Gated Johnson Ranch Nestled on a Rare, Oversized .27 Acre Corner lot offering plenty of room for a Pool! You will fall in love with the Well Appointed Kitchen offering Granite Counters, Gas Cooking, and 42" Cabinets that Opens to Soaring Ceilings in your Living Room with Upgraded Tile Flooring and a Warm Fireplace. Retreat to your Spacious Primary Suite Downstairs with a Walk-In Closet, Double Vanities , Garden Tub, and Separate Shower! Dedicated Study offers a quiet space to work from home! Unwind after a long day on your Covered Patio that's perfect for Stargazing in the Hill Country or for your Fall Texas BBQ's! This convenient location offers an easy drive to San Antonio, Canyon Lake, New Braunfels, and Austin! Outstanding Comal ISD to include the Highly Desirable Smithson Valley HS & Johnson Ranch Elem School in the community. Bulverde Middle School opening minutes away in August 2024! Fabulous Community Amenities include Community Pool and Park. Water Softener! Includes Builder's Structural Warranty that will be Transferred to You for your Peace of Mind as the New Homeowner. Be First to Tour this Gorgeous home!
